Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的雲南茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的抹茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在這裡 學姐你說過我擁有技術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指什麼技術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我明說嗎 當然是推理這門技術…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是偵探 而是推理作家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福爾摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇透福爾摩斯沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本鄉所讀的小說裡夾著便條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我謄了一份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原來以為只是在篩選可能用到的點子
